"title": "5846: enjoyment",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5846: enjoyment",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The ability to find pleasure and joy in life. Scripture sees the capacity for enjoyment as a gift from God, whose people are to find pleasure and happiness in him and the many blessings he has given to them.</p>\n<h2>Human capacity and opportunity for enjoyment is bestowed by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:18-Eccl5:20\">ECC 5:18–5:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:35\">NEH 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24-Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:24–2:26</a></p>\n<h2>People find enjoyment in a great diversity of things</h2>\n<h3>Enjoyment of the land and its produce</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:31\">NUM 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:17-Gen45:18\">GEN 45:17–45:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:6\">DEU 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:30\">DEU 28:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:22\">ISA 65:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:5\">JER 31:5</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of long life and health</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:8\">ECC 11:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:2\">DEU 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:28\">1CH 29:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:16\">PRO 28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:2\">3JN 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of peace and security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:28\">JDG 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3\">PSA 37:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:2\">ACT 24:2</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of prosperity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:4-Ps106:5\">PSA 106:4–106:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:18-Ps37:19\">PSA 37:18–37:19</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of food and drink</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:9-Neh8:12\">NEH 8:9–8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:16\">HAB 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of friendship and fellowship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:24\">ROM 15:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:6\">JDG 19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:9\">JDG 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:22\">JDG 19:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:12-Ps55:14\">PSA 55:12–55:14</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:18\">PRO 7:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:9\">ECC 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of the fruits of righteous living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:10\">ISA 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:2\">PRO 13:2</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of good favour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:45-Acts7:46\">ACT 7:45–7:46</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:22\">ECC 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of light of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:35\">JHN 5:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:28\">JOB 33:28</a></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of hospitality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:23\">ROM 16:23</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:18\">JOB 3:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Enjoyment of fragrance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:38\">EXO 30:38</a></strong></p>\n<h2>People also find unwholesome enjoyment in sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:24-Heb11:25\">HEB 11:24–11:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:12-Job20:14\">JOB 20:12–20:14</a></p>\n<h2>The land enjoying rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:21\">2CH 36:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:34\">LEV 26:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:43\">LEV 26:43</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of enjoyment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:30\">DEU 28:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:17-Job20:19\">JOB 20:17–20:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:23-Job21:25\">JOB 21:23–21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:1-Eccl6:6\">ECC 6:1–6:6</a></p>",
